Marie Wilson (American actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_Wilson_(American_actress) 0 Marie Wilson (born Katherine Elizabeth Wilson; August 19, 1916 – November 23, 1972) was an American radio, film, and television actress. She may be best remembered as the title character in My Friend Irma.
